name: Rooster
misc: Good burgers, has a downstair pub floor.

name: Oluthuone Leskinen
misc: The original after work place of the City. More mature oriented, but culturally significant. Has a large collection of seasonal beers.

name: Snooker Time
misc: A good place if you're looking for a place to talk to strangers.

name: Kuluma
misc: An all-around place. Has everything for everyone. (Tip: next to Kauppuri 5)

name: Heinäpään Oluttupa
misc: A local pub of the unique Heinäpää region, filled with Heinäpää regulars.

name: Letkunpuiston Helmi
misc: A good choice for some after work chilling.

name: Peppers
misc: Never go here. I don't know many people who've entered this place and returned unchanged.
